    • Method Detail

      • parse

        org.spongepowered.api.text.Text parse(Placeholder.Standard placeholder)
        Creates a Text based on the provided Placeholder.Standard.

        This method should not throw an error, instead doing so in validate(Placeholder.Standard) which is called when the Placeholder that will call this is built.

        Parameters:
        placeholder - The Placeholder.Standard
        Returns:
        The Text

      • validate

        default void validate(Placeholder.Standard placeholder)
               throws java.lang.IllegalStateException
        Validates a Placeholder.Standard as its being built. Throw an IllegalStateException if the placeholder will not be valid.
        Parameters:
        placeholder - The newly built Placeholder.Standard
        Throws:
        java.lang.IllegalStateException - if the placeholder is not valid.
